span style=\"color:white;\">o</span>||'''[[Gare de Batz-sur-Mer|Batz-sur-Mer]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Loire-Atlantique|44]]||[[Batz-sur-Mer]]\n|[[TER Pays de la Loire]]\n|- style=\"background:#efefef;\"\n| style=\"background:#0080c0;\" |<span style=\"color:white;\">o</span>||[[gare du Croisic|'''Le Croisic''']]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Loire-Atlantique|44]]||[[Le Croisic]]||[[TGV]], [[Intercit\u00e9s]], [[TER Pays de la Loire]]\n|}\n\n<br />\n\n[[Category:Transport in Centre-Val de Loire]]\n[[Category:Transport express r\u00e9gional]]\n\n\n{{France-rail-transport-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox rail line\n| name                            = Interloire\n| color                           = 0080C0\n| image                           = UM de Regio2N sur l'Interloire pr\u00e8s de La M\u00e9nitr\u00e9 par Cramos.JPG\n| system                          = [[TER Centre-Val de Loire]]<br/>\n[[TER Pays de la Loire]]\n| stations                        = 21\n| open                            = September 25, 1994\n| operator                        = [[SNCF]]\n| stock                           = [[Bombardier Omneo|Z56500]]\n}}\n\nThe '''Interloire''' is a French train service run by [[TER Centre|TER Centre-Val de Loire]] and [[TER Pays de la Loire]] linking [[Orl\u00e9ans]] to [[Le Croisic]] via [[Blois]], [[Saint-Pierre-des-Corps]], [[Saumur]], [[Angers]] and [[Nantes]]. \n\nThe sections Nantes-Angers and [[Tours]]-Orl\u00e9ans are respectively part of the major railway axes Paris-Nantes and Paris-Bordeaux (on the classic lines). The [[electrification]], the bigger [[curve radii]] and the absence of [[level crossings]] make this one of the rare lines with an authorised speed of 200 km/h.\n\nDuring [[weekday]]s, there are on average 3 return journeys per day Orl\u00e9ans-Nantes, of which one is extended to Le Croisic. On [[Workweek|weekends]], the service is more frequent.\n\n== Route ==\nStations in bold are served by every train as they pass through the respective station. \n{| class=\"wikitable\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #999; background:#fff;\"\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#ccc;\"\n!&nbsp;!! Station !![[D\u00e9partements of France|D\u00e9partement]]!! City !! Correspondences\n|-\n| style=\"background:#0080c0;\" |<span style=\"color:white;\">o</span>||[[Gare d'Orl\u00e9ans|'''Orl\u00e9ans''']]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Loiret|45]]||[[Orl\u00e9ans]]||[[Corail (train)|Corail]] (Paris, Vierzon, Limoges)&nbsp;\u2014 {{TER/correspondance|Centre}} (\u00c9tampes, Vierzon)&nbsp;\u2014 [[Tramway d'Orl\u00e9ans]]\n|- style=\"background:#efefef;\"\n| style=\"background:#0080c0;\" |<span style=\"color:white;\">o</span>||[[Gare de Beaugency|Beaugency]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Loiret|45]]||[[Beaugency]]\n|[[TER Centre-Val de Loire]]\n|- \n| style=\"background:#0080c0;\" |<span style=\"color:white;\">o</span>||[[Gare de Blois|'''Blois''']]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Loir-et-Cher|41]]||[[Blois]]||[[Intercit\u00e9s]], [[TER Centre-Val de Loire]]\n|- style=\"background:#efefef;\"\n| style=\"background:#0080c0;\" |<span style=\"color:white;\">o</span>||[[Gare d'Amboise|Amboise]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Indre-et-Loire|37]]||[[Amboise]]||[[TER Centre-Val de Loire]]\n|-\n| style=\"background:#0080c0;\" |<span style=\"color:white;\">o</span>||[[gare de Saint-Pierre-des-Corps|'''Saint-Pierre-des-Corps''']]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Indre-et-Loire|37]]||[[Tours]]|| (Paris, Tours, Bordeaux, Lille)&nbsp;\u2014 {{TER/correspondance|Centre}} (Tours, Poitiers, Loches, Chinon, Vend\u00f4me, Le Mans)\n|- style=\"background:#efefef;\"\n| style=\"background:#0080c0;\" |<span style=\"color:white;\">o</span>||'''[[Gare de Tours|Tours]]'''|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Indre-et-Loire|37]]||[[Tours]]||[[TGV]], [[Intercit\u00e9s]], [[TER Centre-Val de Loire]], [[Tours tramway|Tramway de Tours]]\n|- \n| style=\"background:#0080c0;\" |<span style=\"color:white;\">o