ds]]) - McDermitt\n*Channel 4 (RF channel 34): [[K34PY-D]] - ([[NBC]]/[[This TV]]/[[TBD (TV network)|TBD]]) - Mina/Luning\n*Channel 4 (RF channel 28): [[K28PP-D]] - ([[NBC]]/[[Dabl]]/[[TBD (TV network)|TBD]]) - Shurz\n*Channel 5 (RF channel 15): [[K15LG-D]] - ([[PBS]]/[[Create (TV network)|Create]]/[[PBS Kids]]) - Hawthorne\n*Channel 5 (RF channel 25): [[K25PU-D]] - ([[PBS]]/[[Create (TV network)|Create]]/[[PBS Kids]]) - Mina/Luning\n*Channel 5 (RF channel 18): [[K18NA-D]] - ([[Fox Broadcasting Company|FOX]]/[[Bounce TV]]/[[Court TV Mystery]]/[[Dabl]]) - Pahrump\n*Channel 5 (RF channel 34): [[K44KN-D]] - ([[Fox Broadcasting Company|FOX]]/[[Bounce TV]]/[[Court TV Mystery]]/[[Dabl]]) - Panaca\n*Channel 5 (RF channel 33): [[K45EY-D]] - ([[PBS]]/[[Create (TV network)|Create]]/[[PBS Kids]]) - Round Mountain\n*Channel 5 (RF channel 30): [[K30PB-D]] - ([[PBS]]/[[Create (TV network)|Create]]/[[PBS Kids]]) - Shurz\n*Channel 5 (RF channel 36): [[K47KJ-D]] - ([[PBS]]/[[Create (TV network)|Create]]/[[PBS Kids]]) - Verdi\n*Channel 5 (RF channel 19): [[K38EH-D]] - ([[PBS]]/[[Create (TV network)|Create]]/[[PBS Kids]]) - Walker Lake\n*Channel 7 (RF channel 14): [[K14SE-D]] - ([[NBC]]/News/[[Justice Network]]/[[Quest (American TV network)|Quest]]) - McDermitt\n*Channel 8 (RF channel 22): [[K22DR]] - ([[CBS]]/[[MeTV]]/[[Movies!]]) - Laughlin\n*Channel 8 (RF channel 30): [[K30PR-D]] - ([[CBS]]/[[MeTV]]/[[Movies!]]) - Pahrump\n*Channel 8 (RF channel 28): [[K28PX-D]] - ([[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]/[[MeTV]]/[[The CW Plus|CW+]]) - Stead\n*Channel 8 (RF channel 23): [[K23OK-D]] - ([[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]/[[MeTV]]/[[The CW Plus|CW+]]) - Walker Lake\n*Channel 9 (RF channel 18): [[K18NG-D]] - ([[Fox Broadcasting Corporation|FOX]]/[[MeTV]]/[[Grit (TV network)|Grit]]) - McDermitt\n*Channel 10 (RF channel 36): [[K36PX-D]] - ([[PBS]]/[[Create (TV network)|Create]]/[[PBS Kids]]) - Caliente\n*Channel 10 (RF channel 32): [[K43DS-D]] - ([[PBS]]/[[Create (TV network)|Create]]/[